From b602f1f2d6d4d4197aec137185875ad8b155747f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vinith Kumar R <quic_vinithku@quicinc.com>
Date: Fri, 25 Apr 2025 06:58:00 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] wifi: ath12k: change soc name to device name
Git-commit: b602f1f2d6d4d4197aec137185875ad8b155747f
Patch-mainline: v6.16-rc1
References: jsc#PED-14425

To have consistent nomenclature, replace the use of the term "soc"
with the term "device".

Tested-on: QCN9274 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.WBE.1.1.1-00210-QCAHKSWPL_SILICONZ-1
Tested-on: WCN7850 hw2.0 PCI WLAN.HMT.1.0.c5-00481-QCAHMTSWPL_V1.0_V2.0_SILICONZ-3

Signed-off-by: Vinith Kumar R <quic_vinithku@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Nithyanantham Paramasivam <nithyanantham.paramasivam@oss.qualcomm.com>
Reviewed-by: Mahendran P <quic_mahep@quicinc.com>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20250425012802.698914-2-nithyanantham.paramasivam@oss.qualcomm.com
Signed-off-by: Jeff Johnson <jeff.johnson@oss.qualcomm.com>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
